title: Static Analysis

com.docusign.ink.permission.C2D_MESSAGE.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT.description: This constant was deprecated in API level 28. Applications should request USE_BIOMETRIC instead

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

"consumer_disclosure_offline" : "CONSUMER DISCLOSURE

From time to time, %1$s (we, us or Company) may be required by law to provide to you certain written notices or disclosures. Described below are the terms and conditions for providing to you such notices and disclosures electronically through the DocuSign, Inc. (DocuSign) electronic signing system. Please read the information below carefully and thoroughly, and if you can access this information electronically to your satisfaction and agree to these terms and conditions, please confirm your agreement by clicking the ‘I agree’ button at the bottom of this document.

Getting paper copies

At any time, you may request from us a paper copy of any record provided or made available electronically to you by us. You will have the ability to download and print documents we send to you through the DocuSign system during and immediately after signing session and, if you elect to create a DocuSign signer account, you may access them for a limited period of time (usually 30 days) after such documents are first sent to you. After such time, if you wish for us to send you paper copies of any such documents from our office to you, you will be charged a 0.00 per-page fee. You may request delivery of such paper copies from us by following the procedure described below.

Withdrawing your consent

If you decide to receive notices and disclosures from us electronically, you may at any time change your mind and tell us that thereafter you want to receive required notices and disclosures only in paper format. How you must inform us of your decision to receive future notices and disclosure in paper format and withdraw your consent to receive notices and disclosures electronically is described below.

Consequences of changing your mind

If you elect to receive required notices and disclosures only in paper format, it will slow the speed at which we can complete certain steps in transactions with you and delivering services to you because we will need first to send the required notices or disclosures to you in paper format, and then wait until we receive back from you your acknowledgment of your receipt of such paper notices or disclosures. To indicate to us that you are changing your mind, you must withdraw your consent using the DocuSign ‘Withdraw Consent’ form on the signing page of a DocuSign envelope instead of signing it. This will indicate to us that you have withdrawn your consent to receive required notices and disclosures electronically from us and you will no longer be able to use the DocuSign system to receive required notices and consents electronically from us or to sign electronically documents from us.

All notices and disclosures will be sent to you electronically

Unless you tell us otherwise in accordance with the procedures described herein, we will provide electronically to you through the DocuSign system all required notices, disclosures, authorizations, acknowledgements, and other documents that are required to be provided or made available to you during the course of our relationship with you. To reduce the chance of you inadvertently not receiving any notice or disclosure, we prefer to provide all of the required notices and disclosures to you by the same method and to the same address that you have given us. Thus, you can receive all the disclosures and notices electronically or in paper format through the paper mail delivery system. If you do not agree with this process, please let us know as described below. Please also see the paragraph immediately above that describes the consequences of your electing not to receive delivery of the notices and disclosures electronically from us.

How to contact %2$s:

You may contact us to let us know of your changes as to how we may contact you electronically, to request paper copies of certain information from us, and to withdraw your prior consent to receive notices and disclosures electronically as follows:
To contact us by email send messages to: %3$s

To advise %4$s of your new e-mail address

To let us know of a change in your e-mail address where we should send notices and disclosures electronically to you, you must send an email message to us at %5$s and in the body of such request you must state: your previous e-mail address, your new e-mail address.   We do not require any other information from you to change your email address. 

In addition, you must notify DocuSign, Inc. to arrange for your new email address to be reflected in your DocuSign account by following the process for changing e-mail in the DocuSign system.

To request paper copies from %6$s

To request delivery from us of paper copies of the notices and disclosures previously provided by us to you electronically, you must send us an e-mail to %7$s and in the body of such request you must state your e-mail address, full name, US Postal address, and telephone number. We will bill you for any fees at that time, if any.

To withdraw your consent with %8$s

To inform us that you no longer want to receive future notices and disclosures in electronic format you may:

 i. decline to sign a document from within your DocuSign session, and on the subsequent page, select the check-box indicating you wish to withdraw your consent, or you may;

 ii. send us an e-mail to %9$s and in the body of such request you must state your e-mail, full name, US Postal Address, and telephone number. We do not need any other information from you to withdraw consent. The consequences of your withdrawing consent for online documents will be that transactions may take a longer time to process.

Required hardware and software

Operating Systems: Windows® 2000, Windows® XP, Windows Vista®; Mac OS® X.

Browsers: Final release versions of Internet Explorer® 6.0 or above (Windows only); Mozilla Firefox 2.0 or above (Windows and Mac); Safari™ 3.0 or above (Mac only)
PDF Reader: Acrobat® or similar software may be required to view and print PDF files.
Screen Resolution: 800 x 600 minimum.
Enabled Security Settings: Allow per session cookies
** These minimum requirements are subject to change. If these requirements change, you will be asked to re-accept the disclosure. Pre-release (e.g. beta) versions of operating systems and browsers are not supported.

Acknowledging your access and consent to receive materials electronically

To confirm to us that you can access this information electronically, which will be similar to other electronic notices and disclosures that we will provide to you, please verify that you were able to read this electronic disclosure and that you also were able to print on paper or electronically save this page for your future reference and access or that you were able to e-mail this disclosure and consent to an address where you will be able to print on paper or save it for your future reference and access. Further, if you consent to receiving notices and disclosures exclusively in electronic format on the terms and conditions described above, please let us know by clicking the ‘I agree’ button below.

By checking the ‘I agree’ box, I confirm that:
i. I can access and read this Electronic CONSENT TO ELECTRONIC RECEIPT OF ELECTRONIC CONSUMER DISCLOSURES document; and
ii. I can print on paper the disclosure or save or send the disclosure to a place where I can print it, for future reference and access; and
iii. Until or unless I notify %10$s as described above, I consent to receive from exclusively through electronic means all notices, disclosures, authorizations, acknowledgements, and other documents that are required to be provided or made available to me by  %11$s during the course of my relationship with you.

"PlayStore_full_description" : "Mit weit über 50 Millionen Benutzern ist DocuSign weltweit die am häufigsten verwendete Plattform für elektronische Signaturen und Digital Transaction Management (digitale Transaktionsverwaltung)."
"PlayStore_legality_security_one" : "– Rechtlich bindend – die rechtskräftigen Signaturen von DocuSign entsprechen dem US-Gesetz für elektronische Signaturen (eSign Act)."
"PlayStore_legality_security_three" : "– Dokumente sind verschlüsselt und somit viel sicherer als Papierunterlagen."
"PlayStore_legality_security_two" : "– Sehen Sie in vollständigen Prüfverläufen, wer wann signiert hat."
"PlayStore_more_about_docusign" : "Informationen zu elektronischen Signaturen von DocuSign finden Sie unter https://www.docusign.de/produkte/elektronische-signatur/wie-funktioniert-docusign."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_one" : "– Eingeschränkter Dokumentenversand. Monatlich bis zu 5 Dokumente senden."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_three" : "– Wiederverwendbare Vorlagen zum Standardisieren der Dokumente."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_two" : "– Zugriff auf Basisfelder, Signatur inkl. Datum und Namen einholen."
"PlayStore_questions" : "Bei Fragen oder Feedback wenden Sie sich an uns unter mobilefeedback@docusign.com."
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_three" : "– Mobiles Signieren verwalten: Erinnerungen senden, Dokumente stornieren, vor Ort signieren und Vorlagen nutzen."
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_two" : "– Leistungsstarke Maklerfunktionen inkl. zipForm-Plus-Integration und Webbranding."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description1" : "Mit dieser App-Version scannen Sie Dokumente zum Signieren und Hochladen direkt in DocuSign."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description1" : "Seit diesem Release steht Ihnen eine weitere Sicherheitsebene für die DocuSign-App zur Verfügung, nämlich das Entsperren der App per Fingerabdruck."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description1" : "In diesem Release sind zahlreiche Neuerungen und Bugfixes enthalten."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description4" : "– Optimiertes Laden und Filtern von Dokumenten"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_ACH_payment" : "ACH-Zahlung: Zahlungen während des Signiervorgangs per Android Pay, Kreditkarte oder ACH einholen – schnell und einfach!"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_offline_templates" : "Offlinevorlagen: Auf Vorlagen offline zugreifen. Sie verfassen Dokumente schneller und vereinfachen das Senden häufig genutzter Dokumente."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "In diesem Release können Sie mit der neuen Funktion „Mit Foto signieren” Dokumente offline mit einem Foto Ihrer Signatur abschließen."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description2" : "Mit diesem Release wird außerdem das Offline-Signieren für bereits gesendete Umschläge verbessert."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_title" : "Vereinfachen Sie Ihren Alltag! Probieren Sie das Offline-Signieren in unserer DocuSign-App aus."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description1" : "Ihnen stehen seit unserem aktuellen Release optimierte Signierfunktionen für den Offlinemodus zur Verfügung."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "Die Dokumentensichtbarkeit wird jetzt auch im Offlinemodus unterstützt und die Option „Wiederholen” wurde der Offline-Synchronisierungsfunktion hinzugefügt."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "Zudem wurde die App entsprechend der Datenschutz-Grundverordnung (DSGVO) angepasst und es wurden Bugfixes und Leistungsoptimierungen durchgeführt."
"PlayStore_securely_store" : "– Dokumente sicher speichern und verwalten und ortsunabhängig darauf zugreifen."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_five" : "– Erinnern Sie Unterzeichner an das Signieren – die Signatur wird durch ein einfaches Tippen gesetzt!"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_four" : "– Erhalten Sie Push-Benachrichtigungen in Echtzeit, wenn ein Dokument signiert wurde."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_one" : "– Dokumente dank mobiler Features auf Ihr Mobilgerät importieren und dort vorbereiten."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_seven" : "– Unterzeichnen Sie Unterlagen vor Ort oder aus der Ferne."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_six" : "– Stornieren Sie bereits zum Signieren gesendete Dokumente."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_three" : "– Richten Sie eine Signierreihenfolge und einen Workflow für mehrere Unterzeichner ein."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_two" : "– Markieren Sie für die Unterzeichner die Positionen im Dokument, an denen Signaturen, Initialen oder andere Informationen eingefügt werden sollen."
"PlayStore_short_description" : "Auf Ihrem Gerät hochladen und signieren – Google Docs, Worddokumente, PDFs etc."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_five" : "– E-Mail-Anhang in DocuSign öffnen oder Dokumente aus Clouddiensten wie Dropbox, Box, Google Drive, Evernote und Salesforce importieren."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_four" : "– Unterstützt viele Dateiformate – PDF, Word, Excel, Bilder (JPEG, PNG, TIFF), Text etc."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_one" : "– Dokumente immer kostenlos ausfüllen und signieren."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_three" : "– Personalisierte Signaturen direkt auf dem Android-Gerät erstellen und anpassen."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_two" : "– Fertige Dokumente an Personen senden – per E-Mail, Dropbox, Box, Evernote, Google Drive etc."
"PlayStore_standard_plan_three" : "– Mobiles Signieren verwalten: Erinnerungen senden, Dokumente stornieren, vor Ort signieren und Vorlagen nutzen."
"PlayStore_standard_plan_two" : "– Erweiterte Felder inkl. der beliebtesten Felder von DocuSign."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "Die Zahlung wird nach Bestätigung des Kaufs über Google Play abgerechnet. Abonnements werden automatisch verlängert, wenn die automatische Verlängerung nicht mindestens 24 Stunden vor Ablauf des aktuellen Abonnementzeitraums deaktiviert wurde. Das Konto wird 24 Stunden vor Ablauf des aktuellen Abonnementzeitraums mit den Kosten für die Verlängerung belastet. Abonnements können vom Benutzer verwaltet werden. Die automatische Verlängerung kann nach dem Kauf in den Kontoeinstellungen deaktiviert werden. Die Kündigung des aktuell laufenden Abonnements ist während des aktiven Abonnementzeitraums nicht möglich."

"PlayStore_full_description" : "Met meer dan 50 miljoen gebruikers wereldwijd, is DocuSign het meest gebruikte eSignature en digitale transactiemanagementplatform ter wereld."
"PlayStore_legality_security_one" : "– Juridisch bindend - de rechtsgeldige ondertekening via DocuSign is in overeenstemming met de wet eSign."
"PlayStore_legality_security_three" : "– Documenten worden gecodeerd – veiliger dan papieren documenten."
"PlayStore_legality_security_two" : "– Volledig controletraject om te zien wie wanneer heeft getekend."
"PlayStore_more_about_docusign" : "Op https://www.docusign.com/how-it-works vindt u meer informatie over DocuSign en elektronische handtekeningen."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_one" : "– Onbeperkt documenten verzenden. Verzend tot vijf documenten per maand."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_three" : "– Herbruikbare sjablonen zodat u uw documenten kunt standaardiseren."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_two" : "– Toegang tot essentiële velden. Vraag om handtekening, datum en naam. Vraag om handtekening, datum en naam."
"PlayStore_questions" : "Voor vragen of opmerkingen kunt u via e-mail contact met ons opnemen via mobilefeedback@docusign.com"
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_three" : "– Beheer ondertekening onderweg. Herinneren, ongeldig maken, persoonlijke ondertekening en herbruikbare sjablonen."
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_two" : "– Krachtige functies voor onroerend goed, inclusief zipForm Plus integratie en webbranding."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description1" : "Met deze versie kunt u de app gebruiken om een document te scannen en te uploaden naar DocuSign zodat het kan ondertekend worden!"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description2" : "Daarnaast hebben we de volgende verbeteringen toegevoegd:"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description5" : "– Automatisch invullen op het scherm Aanmelden"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description1" : "Met deze versie kunt u een extra beveiligingsniveau toevoegen aan de DocuSign-app door met uw vingerafdruk de app te ontgrendelen."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description1" : "Deze release bevat talloze verbeteringen en bugfixes."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description3" : "– Selectievakje Groepen kan in offline-ondertekenen worden gebruikt"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_ACH_payment" : "ACH-betaling: word snel betaald door betalingen te innen via Android Pay, creditcard of ACH op het moment van ondertekening."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_offline_templates" : "Offline sjablonen: toegang tot uw sjablonen wanneer u offline bent. Verminder de tijd voor het opstellen van documenten en stroomlijn uw veelgebruikte documenten."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "Deze versie voegt een nieuwe functie toe, genaamd Ondertekenen met Foto, waarmee u documenten offline kunt afronden met een foto-handtekening naar keuze."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description2" : "Deze versie verbetert ook de functionaliteit voor het Offline ondertekenen van enveloppen die al zijn verzonden."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_title" : "We hebben uw leven net wat gemakkelijker gemaakt! Probeer onze nieuwe offline ondertekeningsopties in de DocuSign-app."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description1" : "We hebben met onze nieuwste versie verbeteringen aangebracht aan onze functie Offline ondertekenen."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "We ondersteunen nu Documentzichtbaarheid in Offline, en we hebben de optie 'Opnieuw proberen' aan de Offline synchronisatiefunctie toegevoegd."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "Daarnaast hebben wij updates uitgevoerd aan de app ter ondersteuning van de Algemene verordening gegevensbescherming (AVG), samen met bugfixes en prestatieverbeteringen."
"PlayStore_securely_store" : "– Sla documenten veilig op, beheer ze en krijg toegang ertoe, waar u ook bent."
"PlayStore_send_documents" : "– Verzend documenten zodat anderen ze kunnen ondertekenen."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_five" : "– Herinner met een tik ondertekenaars eraan dat er een document moet worden ondertekend."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_four" : "– Ontvang realtime pushmeldingen wanneer een document is ondertekend."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_one" : "– Met functies voor onderweg kunt u een document importeren en voorbereiden, gewoon vanaf uw apparaat."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_seven" : "– Ondersteunt opties voor zowel persoonlijke ondertekening als voor ondertekening op afstand."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_six" : "– Maak documenten ongeldig die al ter ondertekening zijn verzonden."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_three" : "– Als er meerdere ondertekenaars zijn, kunt u een volgorde en workflow voor het ondertekenen instellen."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_two" : "– Leid uw ondertekenaars met 'Hier ondertekenen'-labels waardoor ze precies weten waar ze moeten ondertekenen, een paraaf zetten of extra informatie toevoegen."
"PlayStore_short_description" : "Upload, teken en verzend Google Docs, Word-documenten, PDF's vanaf uw apparaat."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_five" : "– Open een e-mailbijlage in DocuSign of belangrijke documenten van clouddiensten zoals Dropbox, Google Drive, Box, Evernote en Salesforce."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_four" : "– Ondersteunt PDF, Word, Excel, afbeeldingen (JPEG, PNG, TIFF), tekst en meer."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_one" : "– Vul formulieren in en onderteken ze, gratis. Er is geen maandelijks limiet."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_three" : "– Creëer en personaliseer uw eigen handtekening, gewoon vanaf uw Android-apparaat."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_two" : "– Stuur het ingevulde document naar wie u maar wilt via e-mail, Dropbox, Google Drive, Box, Evernote en andere diensten."
"PlayStore_standard_plan_three" : "– Beheer ondertekening onderweg. Herinneren, ongeldig maken, persoonlijke ondertekening en herbruikbare sjablonen."
"PlayStore_standard_plan_two" : "– Krijg toegang tot geavanceerde velden, inclusief de meest populaire bij DocuSign."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "Het bedrag wordt van het Google Play-account afgeschreven bij bevestiging van de aankoop. Abonnement verlengt automatisch tenzij automatisch verlengen minstens 24 uur voor het eind van de huidige periode is uitgeschakeld. Het account wordt voor verlenging belast binnen 24 uur vóór het einde van de huidige periode, en toont de kosten van de verlenging. Abonnementen kunnen door de eigenaar worden beheerd en automatisch verlengen kan na aankoop worden uitgeschakeld via de Accountinstellingen. Annulering van het huidige abonnement is niet toegestaan tijdens de actieve huidige periode."

"PlayStore_full_description" : "DocuSignは、全世界で5,000万を超えるユーザーに信頼され、最も広く使用されている電子署名およびデジタルトランザクション管理プラットフォームです。"

"PlayStore_personal_plan_one" : "– 制限付きの文書送信。最大で毎月10件の文書を送信可能。"
"PlayStore_personal_plan_three" : "– テンプレート機能による文書作成の標準化。"
"PlayStore_personal_plan_two" : "– DocuSignの基本的なフィールドの使用。署名、署名日、名前などのフィールド。"
"PlayStore_questions" : "DocuSignについてのご質問やご意見は、mobilefeedback@docusign.comまでメールでお寄せください。"
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_three" : "– モバイルデバイスでの文書や署名の管理。リマインダー送信、署名依頼の取り消し、同席での署名、およびテンプレート機能など。"
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_two" : "– zipForm Plusへの統合やブランド設定など、不動産業者専用の機能。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description1" : "このリリースでは、アプリ内で文書を撮影してそれをそのまま新規文書としてDocuSignにアップロードできます。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description2" : "さらに、以下の機能が追加されました。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description5" : "– セットアップ画面での自動入力"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description7" : "– 既存の問題の解決と機能拡張"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description1" : "このリリースでは、DocuSignアプリのロックを解除するときに指紋認証を必須とすることで、アプリ使用時のセキュリティを強化できます。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description3" : "– 標準ベースの署名機能（SBS）のネイティブサポート"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description4" : "– FCMベースのプッシュ通知"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description1" : "このリリースには、多くの機能拡張と問題修正が含まれています。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description2" : "– 電子公証人機能を使用したエンベロープへの署名"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description3" : "– オフライン署名でのチェックボックスグループの使用"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description4" : "– より強固になった文書のロードとフィルター機能"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_ACH_payment" : "ACHによる支払い: Android Pay、クレジットカード、およびACHによる支払いがサポートされます。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_bug_fixes" : "既存の問題の解決と機能拡張"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_offline_templates" : "オフラインテンプレート: オフライン時でもテンプレートにアクセスできます。同じ文書を何度も送信する場合の操作が効率化します。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "このリリースには写真による署名機能が追加されています。自分の署名を撮影して、オフラインでも文書に署名することができます。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description2" : "また、送信済みエンベロープでのオフラインでの署名機能が強化されました。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_title" : "DocuSignアプリがより便利になりました。オフラインでの署名機能をお試しください。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description1" : "最新のリリースでは、オフラインでの署名機能が拡張されています。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "文書の表示条件機能がオフライン時にもサポートされるようになり、またオフライン同期機能に再試行オプションが追加されました。"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "さらに、EU一般データ保護規則（General Data Protection Regulation: GDPR）への準拠、既知の問題の解決、およびパフォーマンスの改善が施されました。"
"PlayStore_securely_store" : "– 自分が送信したり署名したりした文書は安全に保管され、どこからでもアクセスできます。"
"PlayStore_send_documents" : "– 自分以外の署名が必要な場合は、文書を送信して署名を依頼できます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_five" : "– シングルタップで署名者にリマインダーを送信して、署名を催促できます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_four" : "– 署名者が文書に署名すると、差出人にはリアルタイムの通知が送信されます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_one" : "– 手元のモバイルデバイスだけで、いつでもどこでも文書を作成して送信できます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_seven" : "– オンラインでの署名のほか、署名者と同席して署名プロセスを進めることもできます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_six" : "– 送信済みの署名依頼を簡単に取り消すことができます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_three" : "– 複数の署名者を設定して、その署名順序を指定することもできます。"
"PlayStore_sending_documents_two" : "– 署名者は、［ここに署名］などのフィールドの表示に従って簡単に文書に署名したり、イニシャルや必要事項を入力したりできます。"
"PlayStore_short_description" : "Googleドキュメント、Word文書、PDFなど、さまざまな形式の文書をデバイスからアップロードして送信したり署名したりできます。"
"PlayStore_signing_documents_five" : "– DocuSignから、メールに添付されたファイルや、Dropbox、Googleドライブ、Box、Evernote、Salesforceなどのクラウドストレージ上のファイルにアクセスできます。"
"PlayStore_signing_documents_four" : "– PDF、Word、Excel、画像（JPEG、PNG、TIFF）、テキストなど、さまざまなファイル形式がサポートされます。"
"PlayStore_signing_documents_one" : "– オンライン文書への情報の記入や署名は無料です。毎月の制限はありません。"
"PlayStore_signing_documents_three" : "– Androidデバイス上で独自の署名を作成できます。"
"PlayStore_signing_documents_two" : "- 署名した文書を関与者にメールやDropbox、Googleドライブ、Box、Evernoteなどのクラウドストレージを介して送信できます。"
"PlayStore_standard_plan_three" : "– モバイルデバイスでの文書や署名の管理。リマインダー送信、署名依頼の取り消し、同席での署名、およびテンプレート機能など。"
"PlayStore_standard_plan_two" : "– DocuSignの基本的なフィールドおよび高度なフィールドの使用。"

A renovação da conta será cobrada 24 horas antes do final do período atual e será identificado o custo da renovação. "PlayStore_full_description" : "Avec plus 50 millions d’utilisateurs dans le monde entier, DocuSign est la plate‑forme de signatures électroniques et de gestion de transactions numériques la plus largement utilisée dans le monde."
"PlayStore_legality_security_four" : "– DocuSign est conforme aux normes ISO 27001 et SSAE16."

"PlayStore_personal_plan_one" : "– Envoi de documents limité. Envoi de jusqu’à 5 documents par mois."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_three" : "– Modèles réutilisables pour que vous puissiez uniformiser vos documents."
"PlayStore_personal_plan_two" : "– Accès aux champs essentiels. Demande de signature, date et nom."
"PlayStore_questions" : "Pour vos questions ou vos commentaires, écrivez‑nous à mobilefeedback@docusign.com"
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_three" : "– Gestion nomade des signatures. Rappels, invalidation, signature en personne et modèles réutilisables."
"PlayStore_real_estate_plan_two" : "– Fonctionnalités immobilières puissantes y compris l’intégration zipForm Plus et la personnalisation web à votre marque."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description1" : "Avec cette version, vous pouvez utiliser l’application pour numériser et charger un document directement dans DocuSign pour le signer !"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description2" : "En outre, nous avons ajouté les améliorations suivantes :"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.10_description3" : "– Prise en charge des icônes adaptatives"

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description1" : "Avec cette version, vous pouvez ajouter un niveau de sécurité supplémentaire à l’app DocuSign en utilisant vos empreintes digitales pour déverrouiller l’application."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.12_description3" : "– Prise en charge native des signatures conformes"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description1" : "Nous apportons avec cette version de nombreuses améliorations et corrections de bugs."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description2" : "– Vous pouvez désormais signer des enveloppes notariales"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description3" : "– Des groupes de cases à cocher peuvent être utilisés lors de signatures en mode hors ligne"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description4" : "– Chargement et filtrage des documents bien plus fiables"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_ACH_payment" : "Paiement ACH : soyez payé rapidement en recueillant des paiements via Android Pay, ACH ou cartes de paiements, au moment de la signature."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_offline_templates" : "Modèles hors ligne : accédez à vos modèles en mode hors connexion. Réduisez le temps de préparation des documents et rationalisez le processus d’envoi de documents souvent utilisés."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "Cette version ajoute une nouvelle fonctionnalité appelée Signer avec une Photo, vous permettant de compléter des documents en mode hors ligne avec la photo d’une signature de votre choix."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description2" : "Cette version améliore aussi la fonctionnalité de signature hors ligne sur les enveloppes qui ont déjà été envoyées."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_title" : "Nous venons vous faciliter la vie ! Essayez nos nouvelles options de signature hors ligne dans l’app DocuSign."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description1" : "Dans notre dernière version, nous avons amélioré notre fonctionnalité de signature hors ligne."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "Nous prenons maintenant en charge la visibilité des documents hors ligne et nous avons ajouté une option Réessayer à la fonctionnalité de synchronisation hors ligne."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "De plus, nous avons fait des mises à jour sur l’app pour qu’elle prenne en charge le Règlement Général sur la Protection des Données (RGPD) ainsi que des corrections de bugs et améliorations des performances."
"PlayStore_securely_store" : "– Stockez, gérez et accédez à vos documents de manière sécurisée depuis n’importe où."
"PlayStore_send_documents" : "– Envoyez des documents à d’autres personnes pour qu’ils les signent."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_five" : "– D’un simple touché, rappelez les signataires qui doivent signer un document en attente."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_four" : "– Recevez des notifications en direct et en temps réel dès qu’un document a été signé."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_one" : "– Des fonctionnalités nomades vous permettent d’importer et de préparer un document entièrement sur votre appareil."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_seven" : "– Prend en charge les options de signature en personne et à distance."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_six" : "– Invalidez des documents déjà envoyés pour signature."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_three" : "– Définissez un ordre de signature et un flux pour plusieurs signataires."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_two" : "– Guidez vos signataires avec des balises « Signez ici » qui indiquent exactement où il faut signer, parapher, ou ajouter des informations supplémentaires."
"PlayStore_short_description" : "Chargez, signez et envoyez de votre appareil des docs Google, Word, PDF et plus."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_five" : "– Ouvrez une pièce jointe ou des documents importants dans DocuSign à partir de services cloud comme Dropbox, Google Drive, Box, Evernote ou Salesforce."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_four" : "– Prend en charge les formats PDF, Word, Excel, images (JPEG, PNG, TIFF), texte et bien d’autres."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_one" : "– Remplissez et signez des documents gratuitement, il n’y a aucune limite mensuelle."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_three" : "– Créez puis personnalisez votre signature directement depuis votre appareil Android."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_two" : "– Envoyez le document complété à qui que ce soit via e‑mail, Dropbox, Google Drive, Box, Evernote et plus encore."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "Ahora es posible la visibilidad del documento en modo sin conexión y hemos añadido la opción de reintento a la función de sincronización sin conexión."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "Asimismo, hemos realizado actualizaciones en la aplicación a fin de adaptarnos al Reglamento general de protección de datos (RGPD), además de correcciones de errores y mejoras de rendimiento."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "El pago se cobrará a través de Google Play en el momento de la compra. Las suscripciones se renuevan automáticamente a menos que se desactive la renovación automática al menos 24 horas antes de que finalice el periodo actual. La renovación de la cuenta se cobrará en un plazo de 24 horas antes de que finalice el periodo actual y se identificará el coste de la renovación. El usuario puede gestionar las suscripciones, y la renovación automática puede desactivarse desde la configuración de la cuenta del usuario después de la compra. No se permite cancelar la suscripción actual durante el periodo de suscripción activo."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "Questa versione aggiunge una nuova funzionalità chiamata Firma con foto, che ti consente di completare i documenti offline aggiungendo un'immagine a scelta alla tua firma."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "Inoltre, abbiamo aggiornato l'applicazione in modo da supportare il Regolamento generale sulla protezione dei dati (GDPR), oltre a correzioni di bug e miglioramenti delle prestazioni."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "Il pagamento verrà addebitato a Google Play al momento della conferma dell'acquisto. La sottoscrizione sarà rinnovata automaticamente a meno che non venga disattivata al meno 24 ore prima della fine del periodo attuale. Il rinnovo verrà addebitato nell'account nelle 24 ore precedenti la fine del periodo attuale e verrà indicato il costo del rinnovo. Le sottoscrizioni possono essere gestite dall'utente e il rinnovo automatico può essere disattivato dopo l'acquisto dall'utente nelle impostazioni dell'account. Non è consentito l'annullamento della sottoscrizione attuale durante il periodo di sottoscrizione attivo."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "O pagamento será cobrado na sua conta do Google Play mediante confirmação de compra. As subscrições renovam automaticamente a não ser que a opção de renovação automática seja desativada pelo menos 24 horas antes do fim do período atual. A conta será cobrada para renovação dentro de 24 horas antes do fim do período atual e o custo da renovação será identificado. O utilizador pode gerir as subscrições e desativar a renovação automática ao aceder às definições de utilizador após a compra. Não é permitido nenhum cancelamento para a subscrição atual durante o período de subscrição ativo."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description1" : "В этом выпуске исправлены ошибки и добавлено множество улучшений."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description3" : "— При подписании в автономном режиме можно использовать группы флажков"
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.13_description4" : "— Улучшены загрузка документов и их фильтрование"

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_ACH_payment" : "Платежи через автоматизированную клиринговую палату: быстро получайте отплату благодаря запросам платежей через Android Pay, ACH или с кредитных карт в момент подписания."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.6_offline_templates" : "Автономные шаблоны: доступ к шаблонам без подключения к сети. Сократите время подготовки и оптимизируйте отправку самых используемых документов."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description1" : "В этом выпуске появилась новая функция "Подписать с фото", которая позволяет автономно завершать документы с помощью фотографии подписи на ваш выбор."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_description2" : "В этом выпуске также добавлены новые функции автономного подписания для отправленных конвертов."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.8_title" : "Мы сделали вашу жизнь немного проще! Оцените новые возможности автономного подписания документов в приложении DocuSign."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description1" : "В новом выпуске улучшена функция подписания в автономном режиме."
"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description2" : "Теперь в этом режиме поддерживается функция "Доступность документов", а для автономной синхронизации добавлена кнопка "Повторить"."

"PlayStore_release_notes_3.9_description3" : "Кроме этого, мы обновили приложение в соответствии с требованиями Общего регламента по защите данных (GDPR), устранили ошибки и повысили производительность."
"PlayStore_securely_store" : "– Безопасно храните документы и управляйте ими с любого устройства."
"PlayStore_send_documents" : "– Отправляйте документы на подпись другим пользователям."

"PlayStore_sending_documents_four" : "– Получайте push-уведомления о подписании документа в режиме реального времени."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_one" : "– Функции мобильной работы позволяют импортировать и подготавливать документы на мобильном устройстве."
"PlayStore_sending_documents_seven" : "– Оцените возможность личного и удаленного подписания."

"PlayStore_signing_documents_five" : "– Открывайте в DocuSign вложения из сообщений электронной почты или важные документы из облачных служб, включая Dropbox, Google Диск, Box, Evernote и Salesforce."
"PlayStore_signing_documents_four" : "– Поддерживает документы в форматах PDF, Word, Excel, файлы изображений (JPEG, PNG, TIFF), текстовые файлы TXT и др."

"PlayStore_subscription_information_description" : "Платеж будет списан с вашего счета Google Play после подтверждения покупки. Подписка продлевается автоматически, если эта функция не отключена не менее чем за 24 часа до окончания текущего периода. Для продления подписки с вашего счета будет списана соответствующая сумма в течение 24 часов, предшествующих окончанию текущего периода. Подпиской управляет пользователь. Автоматическое продление можно отключить в параметрах учетной записи пользователя после покупки. В течение периода действия подписки ее отмена невозможна."

playstore_details.title: DocuSign - Upload & Sign Docs
playstore_details.description:
We are in the business of saving paper.  With over 50 million users worldwide, DocuSign is the most widely used eSignature and Digital Transaction Management platform in the world.  Our app offers unlimited free signing as well as upgrade options for your business needs.  Change the way you do business today!

UNLIMITED FREE SIGNING  |  Sign documents on the go.

• Step 1: Create your customized signature directly on your device.
• Step 2: Upload documents easily via email, Google Drive, DropBox, Box, Evernote, Salesforce, or photo scanning.
• Step 3: E-sign your documents for free with no monthly limit.


SEND & MANAGE AGREEMENTS  |  Send & manage files straight from your device.

• Step 1:  Import files to prepare and send out for signature directly from your device.
• Step 2: Prepare your document with “Sign Here” tags that show precisely where to sign, initial, or add additional information.  Set the signing order and workflow for multiple signers.  DocuSign supports in-person and remote signing.
• Step 3: Remind signers to sign with a single tap or void a document that has already been sent for signature.
• Step 4: Receive real-time push notifications when a document has been signed.



E-SIGNATURE IS LEGAL & SECURE.
• Legally binding agreements—DocuSign’s complies with the eSign Act.
• Complete audit trail to see who signed when and where.
• Documents are encrypted—safer and more secure than paper.
• DocuSign is ISO 27001 SSAE16 compliant.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In addition to our free signing experience, we offer advanced features through our premium plans, take a look and see which plan might be right for you:

Standard Plan
• Send documents out for signature.
• Access to advanced fields including DocuSign’s most popular.
• Manage signing on-the-go. Remind, void, in-person signing, and reusable templates.

Real Estate Plan
• Send documents out for signature.
• Powerful real estate features including zipForm Plus integration and web branding.
• Managing signing on-the-go. Remind, void, in-person signing, and reusable templates.

Personal Plan
• Limited document sending. Send up to 5 documents monthly.
• Access to essential fields. Request signature, date, and name.
• Reusable templates so you can standardize your documents.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Supported file types:
• PDF
• Word
• Excel
• Images (JPEG, PNG, TIFF)
• Text
+ more

Common documents to sign with DocuSign
• NDAs
• Sales contracts
• Health care documents
• Financial agreements
• Waivers
• Permission slips
• Lease agreements

For questions or feedback email us:
mobilefeedback@docusign.com

Find out more about DocuSign and electronic signatures: https://www.docusign.com/products/electronic-signature/how-docusign-works

Subscription information: 
Payment will be charged to Google Play at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's account settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period.
